title: Dustin Lynch Stops By And Performs His Hits + Bobby’s Mailbag: Spin Class 'Cheating' + New Artist Tiera Covers ‘Ring of Fire’!
itunes:title: Dustin Lynch Stops By And Performs His Hits + Bobby’s Mailbag: Spin Class 'Cheating' + New Artist Tiera Covers ‘Ring of Fire’!
description:
Dustin Lynch stops by with Mackenzie Porter to perform their new duet. He also plays his first and last hit. Bobby has an email from a wife whose husband started taking a spin class and admits to checking out other women. She wants to know if it’s cheating. New Artist Tiera stops by to perform a really cool cover of “Ring of Fire” and along with a couple of her originals.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
